<title>NA HERHNAK BANG ZAANG KAN CHAP LAI CH67</title>
<key>Db</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ral le tihnak a nai tikah, Ka hna nih a theih a thawng kha, &quot;Na
 herhnak bang zaang kan chap lai,&quot; Khamhbawi Jesuh nih a ka chimh.

[C1]
   A bia ka ral lung hau a si, Khi bia ah keimah nih kaa dor; Nangmah
   na nun a sau bangin, &quot;Na herhnak bang zaang kan chap lai.&quot;

[V2]
 Hi bang biakam ka hmuh lioah Ka lung chung hna a ngam zungzal,
 Zeitintiah na nun chung vial te, &quot;Na herhnak bang zaang kan chap lai.&quot;

[C2]
   A bia ka ral lung hau a si, Khi bia ah keimah nih kaa dor; Nangmah
   na nun a sau bangin, &quot;Na herhnak bang zaang kan chap lai.&quot;

[V3]
 Ka thihnak caan a nai tikah Ka zumh rih lai, na biakam kha, Ka zumh
 bang in ka nun lioah, &quot;Na herhnak bang zaang kan chap lai.&quot;

[C3]
   A bia ka ral lung hau a si, Khi bia ah keimah nih kaa dor; Nangmah
   na nun a sau bangin, &quot;Na herhnak bang zaang kan chap lai.&quot;</lyrics>
</song>